Class Tile

java.lang.Object
Tile
public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
The class for the tile. Each int type for the tile can have 7 values 0 = empty tile 1 = wall 2 = player on tile 3 = moving enemy on tile 4 = stationary enemy on tile 5 = reward on tile 6 = bonus reward on tile 7 = end door on tile
